<p>This privacy policy relates to the pages hosted on the Ning.com network, aliased as studentbox.com.au, which has been created to hold and maintain services and content relating to the "Studentbox". This service aims to make the lives of year 10, 11 &amp; 12 students easier. This service and related information can also be accessed by parents, guardians, teachers and others, as well as any individual that Curtin University ("Curtin University is a trademark of Curtin University of Technology") deems appropriate.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Collected information</h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 style="margin-bottom:15px;">Anonymous information</h3>
<p>You can visit the site to read information of interest to Western Australian high schools students in year 10, 11 and 12, without telling us who you are and without revealing any personal information. To improve the usefulness of the site, we measure and analyse non-identifying, aggregate usage, and volume statistical information from site visitors in order to administer the site, and to constantly improve the quality of our service and site performance, such as providing more relevant content to you during your visit(s)</p>
<p>Information gathered may include, but is not limited to, the following: the activity of the site visitors browser when the visitor is viewing the site; the site path of visitors; general information regarding the visitor's internet service provider and host, and the time visitors come to the site. Please note that this is not personal information, only general summaries of our visitors usage of the site.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 style="margin-bottom:15px;">Personally identifiable information</h3>
<p>When registering with the studentbox.com.au website your personal information will be collected. The personal information collected includes: your first and last name, postcode, school, school year, mobile phone, and School Curriculum and Standards Authority (SCSA) number.</p>
<p>We may also collect log-in information, such as user name and passwords, for internal users that log-in to restricted areas on the site.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 style="margin-bottom:15px;">Information use and disclosure</h3>
<p>All personal identifiable and anonymous information submitted via the studentbox.com.au website (hosted via the Ning network) will be hosted in servers owned by the Ning network located in the United States of America. <a href="http://www.ning.com/privacy/">Ning’s privacy policy</a> is available from their website.</p>
